init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look around, and see a tiny bee, no bigger than a thumb, wearing a tiny crown.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're a little confused, but you decide to play along.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I cannot do that, said the little bee, we need your help.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We need you to find the queen bee.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We need you to find her and bring her back.
